## SI18n

This `SI18n` class allows you to translate easily your websites/apps through an nice and elegant solution.
It can be used in node as well as in the browser and handle things like:

- Specify the languages you support
- Set the default language as fallback
- Automatically detect and apply the user language (in the browser)
- Load and switch between languages with easy
- Easy to integrate with other libraries/frameworks

